reviews.review_text: Ouch... Decent 83 show, but this recording is distorted at times.  Can't really listen to it.

THE BAND LOVES THE SPECTRUM YOU CAN ADD THIS SHOW TO THE MANY,MANY FINE SHOWS THAT WERE PLAYED IN PHILLY.EVEN FOR THE END OF A LONG REAL NICE TOUR.THIS SHOW SMOKED FROM START TO END.AGAIN THE BAND LOVED PHILADELPHIA AND WE LOVED THEM FOR THAT.

Who cares Who cares about the quality of this recording 
It adds character 
This show and the 2 meadoelands show are both in the top 100 ever
GDTRFB Good 83 show.  The highlight is Going Down the Road Feeling Bad, the best version post 75...no soundboard exists, however this audience  recording is very listenable
My very first show. 16 years old and innocent as could be... this one will always be special to me. :)
